			>
			<DIV>Dejavu - I'd like to see a melee proc that lets the next spell you&nbsp;cast fire off twice.&nbsp; GoMish</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Weapon of Magic - Also like to see a spell we can cast on our&nbsp;weapons that imbue it with pure magic, hits unreal hard, and uses mana on each hit, not swing.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Something like Pyromancy (which i love, buts gets me in more trouble than i like) - A nuke that triggers off&nbsp;a dot, fire would be cool.&nbsp; When it triggers and lands its hits weak, 10 damage, last for 5-6 ticks.&nbsp; Nuke again with same spell, adds to the dot, 50 damage, so now we have a 50 dot on the mob which restarts its 5-6 tick countdown, and a 1000 point DD nuke perhaps.&nbsp; Same nuke adds 50-100 more, rinse and repeat that.&nbsp; Long mobs like vish it would get pretty crazy so may have to limit the adding or what not.&nbsp; You devs can figure that out.&nbsp; Call it Pyro 2 /shrug.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Harvest that gives us 5000 mana, but then is a 50-100 mana drain per tick&nbsp;for 15 mins give or take.&nbsp; Like those melee AAs that let them hit hard but then they are weaker after the ability is over.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>To keep the player at the PC watching the game.&nbsp; If the player gets nuked by a spell they know, they can recast on mob instantly if they hit the hotkey before the 6 song buff fades.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>AE that makes all nukers in the raid nuker a lil harder or faster, similar to the zerker thing.</DIV>
