		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			Rune of Arcanium<br><br>This ability allows the wizard to create an arcane rune on the ground around themself. While standing inside the rune, the wizard's spells will become more powerful. Doing more damage as well as casting slightly faster. The effect can be increased if multiple wizards use the rune in range of the other wizard's rune. However when many runes are combined, the stress of maintaining their each individual rune takes a toll on the wizard's stamina. If the wizard should lose all stamina, then their rune will be canceled.<br><div></div>	
		</td></tr>
